ORbJht0yvh0.description:
We are kicking 2020 to the curb and saying HELLO to 2021!
Join us for our 30 Day January Challenge. For the next 30 days we are committing to celebrating our mind and bodies through dance, music, and movement! We are throwing away unrealistic resolutions and expectations and giving you 30 days of things you can actually stick to! After the 30 days, you’ll have everything you need to continue experiencing the JOY in moving your body!

Download the calendar here! https://thefitnessmarshall.org/lifestyle/30-day-challenge-january-2021

HOW TO JOIN THE CHALLENGE
1. Head to youtube.com/thefitnessmarshall
2. Find the section labeled “30 DAY JANUARY CHALLENGE:
3. Click on the playlist of the day
4. Complete all the videos on that playlist (some days might only have one video)
5. Post on social media tagging #thefitnessmarshall @thefitnessmarshall @adflorea @haleyjordan so we can interact with your posts!

GIVEAWAY!!
At the end of the challenge, post a pic with a caption explaining how the challenge impacted you! We aren't looking for before and after photos because that is NOT the point of this challenge. We are creating heathy habits that CELEBRATE you, not shame you. We will pick 3 of our favorite stories to win a piece of our Active Booty Collection and an autographed card from Team Fitness Marshall!!
